the last inhabitant ( armenian : վերջին բնակիչը ) a film by jivan avetisyan ․ co-production by five countries including , armenia , lithuania , sweden , lebanon and us .   the premiere in armenia took place in the framework of the 13th golden apricot yerevan international film festival ( gaiff ) , where the film was presented in the category of armenian panorama .   the release date in armenia will be november 17 , 2016 at three major theaters including , cinemastar , kinopark and moscow cinema .